    "long_instructions": "### Bring Noah's Vision to Life \r\nNoah is in a groove and really wants to use the `Reggaeton Beat` and the `Groovy Beat Two` throughout his song. \r\n\r\n**Noah's Notes:** \r\n- He wants you to add bass, leads, and effects to make his song come to life. \r\n- His only requirements is that the Reggaeton Beat starts the song off for the first 6 measures, then the Groovy Beat comes in for 4 measures, and then the Reggaeton Beat comes back for 2 measures. ",
